                    <td>Community space and code space management system. Manages community spaces, event scheduling, member projects, resource allocation, and collaborative learning. Features maker-space tracking and project showcases.</td>
                    <td><code>CSC</code> Controller</td>
                    <td><a href="Documentation/controllers/CSC.tt" class="doc-link">📄 MISSING DOCS</a> | Controller: <code>CSC.pm</code></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>USBM (Bureau/Management)</strong></td>
