        <h4>🔧 Technical Changes (60+ Code Changes)</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Message Persistence Root Cause:</strong> Metadata field passed as Perl hashref instead of JSON-encoded string. Fixed in both `/ai/result` and `/ai/generate` endpoints (60+ lines of metadata JSON encoding + logging)</li>
            <li><strong>JSON Body Parsing:</strong> Enhanced conditional parsing for JSON vs. form-encoded data with fallback methods and comprehensive debug logging (120+ lines with 15+ debug statements)</li>
            <li><strong>Credentials Fix:</strong> Added `credentials: 'include'` to both widget and `/ai` page fetch requests (2 lines, major functionality improvement)</li>
            <li><strong>UI Improvements:</strong> Conversations list compact layout (110+ lines, 70-80% space reduction), icon rendering fixes (ASCII-based system for universal compatibility)</li>
            <li><strong>Documentation Enhancements:</strong> Comprehensive audit logging system, filename convention documentation, enforcement rules</li>
        </ul>
